title: merry go round of life (Howl's Moving Castle but is it okay if it's lofi hiphop?)
description:
merry go round of life lofi.

***This one got a copyright claim. You can use it if you're fine with revenue sharing with the original copyright owner***

Was planning to turn it into a 4/4 remix initially and thought it would work like my isabella's lullaby remix but it sounds so weird lol.
I also have a first artwork before this, it's the castle itself but I had to drop it because it was so hard and will take a lot of time as you need to use a lot of layers for the elements and textures. I do my artwork on Photoshop and via Pen Tool so you really need to be decisive when making a decision on what's on top and what's on bottom and what's clipping otherwise you'd end up getting really frustrated because it'll be a mess. The Castle got a lot of elements which I really can't get myself to work with but I did, at first. As expected, there are a few errors. Errors on my artwork are usually not a common problem of mine but since It's bigger this time, I really had to drop it, time's moving.
